// ================================
// INVENTORY CONTEXT - BACKEND READY
// ================================
// 
// This context manages inventory state locally using localStorage.
// For backend integration, replace localStorage operations with API calls.
//
// BACKEND INTEGRATION POINTS:
// 1. Replace localStorage.getItem/setItem with API calls
// 2. Update addItem to POST /api/inventory
// 3. Update updateItem to PUT /api/inventory/:id
// 4. Update deleteItem to DELETE /api/inventory/:id
// 5. Update searchItems to GET /api/inventory?search=query
// 6. Update filterByCategory to GET /api/inventory?category=name
// 7. Add error handling for API failures
// 8. Add loading states for async operations
//
// API ENDPOINTS TO IMPLEMENT:
// - GET /api/inventory - Get all items
// - POST /api/inventory - Create new item
